[11.317930] (control) StdoutLine: {'line': b'3: +  geometry_msgs::msg::PoseStamped & posee)\n'}
[11.317977] (control) StdoutLine: {'line': b'3: +{\n'}
[11.318021] (control) StdoutLine: {'line': b'3: +  /**\n'}
