[11.318762] (control) StdoutLine: {'line': b'3: +  bool was_descending = false, trying_descending = false;\n'}
[11.318808] (control) StdoutLine: {'line': b'3: +\n'}
[11.318853] (control) StdoutLine: {'line': b'3: +  while (rclcpp::ok()) {\n'}
[11.318899] (control) StdoutLine: {'line': b'3: +    pose.pose.position.x = posee.pose.position.x;\n'}
