[11.461009] (control) StdoutLine: {'line': b'3: -            stop_cmd.twist.linear.y = 0.0;\n'}
[11.461048] (control) StdoutLine: {'line': b'3: -            stop_cmd.twist.linear.z = 0.0;\n'}
[11.461089] (control) StdoutLine: {'line': b'3: -            node->publishLocalVelocity(stop_cmd);\n'}
[11.461126] (control) StdoutLine: {'line': b'3: -            \n'}
