[11.464754] (control) StdoutLine: {'line': b'3: -            \n'}
[11.464798] (control) StdoutLine: {'line': b'3: -            // Get current pose and heading for global frame velocity\n'}
[11.464839] (control) StdoutLine: {'line': b'3: -            geometry_msgs::msg::PoseStamped current_pose = node->getCurrentLocalPose();\n'}
